Describe the shared responsibility and the defense in-depth security models.
On-premises - Organizations are 100% responsible
Cloud based services - Responsibility shared between customer and cloud provider

Cloud-based services:
Responsibilities are shared depending on where the workload is hosted:
- Software as a Service (SaaS)
- Platform as a Service (PaaS)
- Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS)
- On-premises datacenter

